<paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Garamond" size="240" color="000000">Thank you for entering our Sweet 16 prediction contest. Be sure to remember your user name (</font><font face="Garamond" size="240" color="000000"><field name="Sw16EntryScreen:UserName"/></font><font face="Garamond" size="240" color="000000">) so you can check back to see the leaderboard as the tournament progresses.</font></paragraph>
</xmlData>
<htmlData>
<![CDATA[<p style="margin-left:0pt" align="left">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left:0pt" align="left"><span style="font-family:'Garamond';font-size:12pt;color:#000000">Thank you for entering our Sweet 16 prediction contest. Be sure to remember your user name (</span><span style="font-family:'Garamond';font-size:12pt;color:#000000">&lt;&lt;Sw16EntryScreen:UserName&gt;&gt;</span><span style="font-family:'Garamond';font-size:12pt;color:#000000">) so you can check back to see the leaderboard as the tournament progresses.</span></p>]]>
